aboutDescription: Hello! My name is Vaibhav and I am a Software Engineer from California State University - Monterey Bay. I will be graduating with my Bachelor's degree in Computer Science in Fall 2020. In summer 2020, I am interning as a Web Application Developer at SeeFood App, and I cannot wait for my next journey. I'm most passionate about giving back to the community, and my goal is to pursue this passion within the field of front-end development!
